  "text": "In all experiments we used the ADAM optimizer with a weight decay value of 4 × 10 −4 and batch size 128. All experiments ran at most 80 epochs with a learning rate drop by 70% after 35 epochs and a batch memory of length 3. We used higher learning rates for the embedding layer as specified by defaults in Cakir et al. [CITATION_1] .",
